# Omega Design System

## Radix Theme Components (always prefer these)
- **Layout**: `Box`, `Container`, `Section`, `Flex`, `Grid`, `Inset` (use `Box asChild` for semantic HTML tags)
- **Typography**: `Text`, `Heading`, `Code`, `Kbd`, `Link`, `Strong`, `Em`
- **Interactive**: `Button`, `IconButton`, `TextField`, `TextArea`, `Select`, `Checkbox`, `Switch`, `Slider`
- **Overlay**: `Dialog`, `Popover`, `Tooltip`, `DropdownMenu`
- **Feedback**: `Separator` for dividers

## Custom Components (use instead of building ad-hoc)
- `BentoGrid` + `BentoCell` — for feature grids with 1px-gap bento layout
- `GlowCard` — for content cards with hover glow and optional gradient border
- `LogoTicker` — for infinite-scroll logo/brand marquees
- `MetricRibbon` — for scrolling stats/metric tickers
- `CodeBlock` — for syntax-highlighted code with copy, line highlights, and file headers
- `WireDiagram` — for interactive protocol/architecture diagrams with step animations
- `InteractiveWireDemo` — signature wire-compression visualization (pipe with flowing particles: raw → compressed)
- `AnimatedTerminal` — for typing-effect terminal demos
- `StaggerReveal` — for staggered scroll-reveal of child elements
- `ProductCard` — for product showcase cards with badge, terminal, and CTAs

## CSS Classes (from globals.css)
- **Cards**: `.glass-card`, `.glow-card`, `.gradient-border`
- **Bento**: `.bento-grid`, `.bento-cell`, `.bento-span-2`, `.bento-span-3`, `.bento-span-row-2`, `.bento-card-feature`, `.bento-card`
- **Elevation**: `.elevation-1` through `.elevation-4`; tokens `--shadow-sm`, `--shadow-md`, `--shadow-lg`, `--shadow-glow`
- **Dividers**: `.divider-subtle`, `.divider-gradient`, `.section-divider` (animated gradient between sections)
- **Glow**: `.glow-accent` (configurable via `--glow-color`)
- **Chrome effects**: `.btn-chrome` (dark gunmetal CTA), `.chrome-text` (dramatic sweep), `.chrome-text-subtle` (section headings)
- **Animation**: `.float`, `.pulse-arrow`, `.shimmer-badge`, `.reveal-up`, `.reveal-fade`, `.reveal-slide-up`, `.reveal-slide-left`, `.reveal-slide-right`, `.reveal-scale`
- **Text**: `.stat-glow`, `.overline` (mono uppercase label), `.display-heading` (thin large heading)
- **Tickers**: `.ticker-scroll`, `.logo-ticker-track`
- **Section**: `.section-movement`, `.section-alt`, `.section-hero-gradient`
- **Code**: `.code-block`, `.code-keyword`, `.code-string`, `.code-comment`, `.code-line-highlight`
- **Diagram**: `.diagram-node`, `.diagram-edge`
- **Texture**: `.noise-overlay::after`

## Brand tokens (CSS custom properties)
- `--omega-bg`, `--omega-fg`, `--omega-accent`, `--omega-border`, `--omega-border-hover`
- `--omega-success` (grass-9), `--omega-error` (red-9), `--omega-interactive` (sand-11)
- All `--gray-*` map to `--sand-*` for warm neutral palette

## Typography
- Display/headings: `var(--font-outfit)` — weight 250–300, tracking -0.03em to -0.04em
- Body: `var(--font-outfit)` — weight 400, line-height 1.65–1.7
- Code/labels: `var(--font-jetbrains-mono)` — 11–13px, tracking 0.02–0.12em

## Rules
- Do NOT use raw `div`, `p`, `h1`–`h6` when Radix provides equivalent
- Do NOT use inline colors; use `var(--gray-*)` or brand tokens
- Do NOT introduce external UI libraries
- CTAs use `className="btn-chrome"` for primary actions
- Product names: always "Omega Boost", "Omega Code", "Omega Chat" (never ω prefix in product text)
- Command syntax: `bun run omega-boost` / `bun run omega-code` (not npx)

## Example
```tsx
<Flex gap="3" align="center">
  <Code size="3">bun run omega-code</Code>
  <Button size="3" className="btn-chrome">Copy</Button>
</Flex>
